name: Waachy
overview:
Waachy.com is an online specialty shop that sells rare and unique watches also available in bulk purchasing.

I’m Don Martenson founder of Waachy. I started this online shop in December of 2011. I have been selling rare finds online for years and decided to open an online shop to showcase these great finds to the public. I have recently started a beta service called Try It Before You Buy It. This service is a way to fill the void of shopping online and being forced to pay for an item before you can even see and hold it. This service will allow our customers the ability to checkout any item for free and we will ship it to them for free. The customer will have up to 3 business days after receiving the item to test it out and when they are ready they can purchase the item.
